title: Khugajwng gwswjwng  sannai maonai jwng
lyrics:
Khugajwng gwswjwng  sannai maonai jwng
Jwng nwngni sigangao udayee jabai -2
Jwngkhou nimaha hwdw -2
(A)
Jwng papi blabw, simang nuyw jwng
Swrgwao Arphoni gelenaikhou
Jwng rwnga blabw, hastayw jwng
Dhwrwm huda badi khulumlangnw -2
Jwngni binaikhou nwng khwnasongdw
Jwngkhou nwngni serao dwn -2
